{
  "stem": "24615.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four girls and three boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, 23, 23, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because we were alone, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I didn't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just me and my wife, you know, and I was alone since I was 13 years old, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got married when I was 30, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think she is a survivor, but she came here before-- maybe a year before the war broke out with the Germans, I guess.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll tell you, we didn't even decide, it just happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- in-- in the beginning, we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got married, we-- we came-- we came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went for our honeymoon to New York for a few days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came back, we didn't even have a place for to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we stayed with my cousin for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after we find our apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked in a-- when I came, I got laid off where I worked for the market.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I was real, real-- a Jewish person, you know, I just got-- and I only had $50, you know, what, when I came, they gave me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't have where to stay, nothing, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after, I found in another place, another market of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he played the horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- he played-- he gambled, so he lost the market, so I got laid off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't pay us so after, we went to the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know what they collect the money, you know, if the employer don't pay you?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told us it might take a little long, you know, you collect the money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they collected the money for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a few hundred dollars.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
